OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGrenfell Tower: Builders   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'gaming system' to avoid   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffire safety rules          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Housebuilders may be "gaming the       
OL,6, system" to avoid fire safety checks put
OL,7, in place after the Grenfell Tower fire,
OL,8, London Fire Brigade (LFB) has warned.  
OL,10,FDeputy Commissioner Paul Jennings said 
OL,11,Fthere are "hundreds if not thousands"  
OL,12,Fof new buildings which may be          
OL,13,F"deliberately" designed to avoid rules.
OL,15,FThey include blocks designed to be     
OL,16,Flower than an 18m (59ft) limit to be   
OL,17,Fconsidered a high-rise building.       
OL,19,FThe building safety minister branded   
OL,20,Fefforts to "cut corners" as "shocking".
